drm/i915: Use ERR_CAST instead of ERR_PTR(PTR_ERR())

Fix following coccicheck warning:
./drivers/gpu/drm/i915/gem/i915_gem_execbuffer.c:3117:15-22: WARNING:
ERR_CAST can be used with eb->requests[i].

